Package model

Class GameMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • model.GameMap
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Map_Easy, Map_Hard, Map_Intermediate

    public abstract class GameMap
extends java.util.Observable
    this is the model of the map with extensions for each of the difficulties. it is observed by the view and determines what gets drawn where. stores every tile on the map along with each tower and enemy.
